I don't know.

00:04:17.950 --> 00:04:20.696
So whether they get it, like
whether after the tests,

00:04:20.696 --> 00:04:23.070
you've given a test, and you
go, man, that student really

00:04:23.070 --> 00:04:23.730
got it.

00:04:23.730 --> 00:04:27.300
That student really
gets this material,

00:04:27.300 --> 00:04:31.440
and whether they passed the
exam or failed the exam.

00:04:31.440 --> 00:04:34.260
So the size of the
circle is more or less

00:04:34.260 --> 00:04:39.132
the number of people that
fall into those quadrants.

