00:06:01.416 --> 00:06:02.290
with multiple choice.

00:06:02.290 --> 00:06:05.225
So you could easily pass just
with good test-taking skills

00:06:05.225 --> 00:06:06.081
or a good memory.

00:06:06.081 --> 00:06:07.080
JANET RANKIN: Excellent.

00:06:07.080 --> 00:06:09.330
So you pass with sort of
good test taking skills.

00:06:09.330 --> 00:06:11.460
Now I want us to
hang on to that.

00:06:11.460 --> 00:06:15.060
There's an underlying
assumption in Dave's comment.

00:06:15.060 --> 00:06:17.000
So I'd like to hang
on to that thought,

00:06:17.000 --> 00:06:19.857
but let's hear a few
other conjectures and see.

