People don't generally get it.

00:12:36.870 --> 00:12:39.720
They get the fact that it
has to do with sorting,

00:12:39.720 --> 00:12:43.380
and some planning,
some arranging things,

00:12:43.380 --> 00:12:46.190
but they don't get that
it's about the laundry.

00:12:46.190 --> 00:12:48.660
If you skim it-- you don't
have to totally reread it--

00:12:48.660 --> 00:12:51.450
but if you skim it
with the idea that it's

00:12:51.450 --> 00:12:55.290
about doing the
laundry, you probably

00:12:55.290 --> 00:13:03.860
can understand it better, maybe.

