They're not from your point
of view, as we mentioned.

00:34:06.680 --> 00:34:08.179
They're not what
you're going to do.

00:34:08.179 --> 00:34:10.345
I'm going to introduce
students to the major turning

00:34:10.345 --> 00:34:13.747
points and processes in
