AUDIENCE: Describe.

00:36:43.770 --> 00:36:46.810
JANET RANKIN:
Describe how, sure.

00:36:49.970 --> 00:36:50.695
Anything else?

00:36:50.695 --> 00:36:52.445
AUDIENCE: [INAUDIBLE]
it seems like you're

00:36:52.445 --> 00:36:54.905
trying to get [INAUDIBLE].

00:36:54.905 --> 00:36:57.030
JANET RANKIN: Right.

00:36:57.030 --> 00:36:58.720
So that's a great
point, is that we

00:36:58.720 --> 00:37:05.020
don't know where this faculty
member put this on their table.

