We don't know whether
it really just states

00:37:07.370 --> 00:37:11.590
some ways that, list some ways
that these things have affected

00:37:11.590 --> 00:37:15.790
Americans, North Americans'
lives, or Americans' lives--

00:37:15.790 --> 00:37:18.580
which is kind of a remember
thing, just make a list--

00:37:18.580 --> 00:37:22.780
or whether it's do some
analysis on some situation.

00:37:22.780 --> 00:37:25.120
We don't know that, but
