or not they understand.

00:43:14.470 --> 00:43:17.470
And you as the
instructor can see it.

00:43:17.470 --> 00:43:20.080
If I walk around,
if I listen, if I

00:43:20.080 --> 00:43:23.680
look at who answered what
question on the clickers,

00:43:23.680 --> 00:43:26.320
or on the raising your hand,
multiple choice questions,

00:43:26.320 --> 00:43:30.320
