here, I get a better,

00:43:30.320 --> 00:43:32.290
a much better sense
of who understands

00:43:32.290 --> 00:43:33.580
or doesn't understand.

00:43:33.580 --> 00:43:38.710
If all I'm doing is
lecturing I can't tell.

00:43:38.710 --> 00:43:41.530
And I can ask do you
understand, but they're not

00:43:41.530 --> 00:43:43.480
